headline: Camden Property Trust Announces Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Release and Conference Call Dates
summary: HOUSTON, July 08, 2025--Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") announced today that its second quarter 2025 earnings will be released after the market closes on Thursday, July 31, 2025. Management will host a conference call on the following day, Friday, August 1, 2025, at 10:00 AM Central Time.
